  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE NURSE PRACTITIONERS TO SERVE AS THE CERTIFYING PHYSICIAN FOR THE PURPOSE OF COMPREHENSIVE MANAGEMENT OF A PATIENT'S DIABETES IF THE NURSE PRACTITIONER IS PRACTICING INCIDENT TO THE PHYSICIAN WITH WHOM THE NURSE PRACTITIONER HAS A COLLABORATIVE RELATIONSHIP, AND TO PRESCRIBE THERAPEUTIC SHOES, MODIFICATIONS AND INSERTS FOR PATIENTS WITH DIABETES, IN ACCORDANCE WITH RULES AND OTHER GUIDELINES FROM THE CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
